title: Hong Kong GDP Constant Prices
description: GDP Constant Prices in Hong Kong increased to 689915 HKD Million in the third quarter of 2022 from 668074 HKD Million in the second quarter of 2022. GDP Constant Prices in Hong Kong averaged 380754.41 HKD Million from 1973 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 766684 HKD Million in the fourth quarter of 2018 and a record low of 74856 HKD Million in the fourth quarter of 1974. This page provides - Hong Kong GDP Constant Prices - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Census and Statistics Department, Hong Kong
